data.title: About Ebby Halliday's Southwest Dallas
data.meta_description: Ebby Halliday's Southwest Dallas office location offers easy access to IH 35, IH 20, IH 45 and Highway 67. Just 30 minutes south of DFW International Airport, our office serves a mature neighborhood located in a quiet suburban-living environment at the doorstep of Joe Pool Lake. The rolling hills, soothing creeks, and many trees help to maintain a real "hometown" atmosphere with convenient access to the Metroplex and 15-minute commute to downtown Dallas.
data.text:
Ebby’s Southwest Dallas Office at 905 N. U.S. Highway 67, Suite 100, in Cedar Hill was built for the future. It offers an exceptional location and is a statement of the Ebby Halliday Companies’ commitment to serving the Southern Sector for years to come.

“As a company, we recognized that the Southern Sector was underserved by residential real estate brokerages and their affiliated services, such as mortgage, insurance and title,” says Pamela Young, sales leader of Ebby’s Southwest Dallas Office. “We are actively expanding our presence, increasing homeownership opportunities and providing expert representation for the area’s buyers and sellers. As part of this commitment, we are dedicated to expanding the diversity of our employees and sales force.”

Ebby’s Southwest Dallas team enjoys a spacious, modern environment that includes cutting-edge technology, conference rooms, a well-appointed training room and private phone rooms, all in an open-concept office.

“Our Southwest Dallas office offers new and experienced agents a sophisticated atmosphere and the latest technology in a much-sought-after Cedar Hill location,” says Young. “If you’re interested in speaking further about opportunities to grow your residential real estate career, please contact me today.”

Adds Young, “We’re proud of our commitment to this beautiful part of North Texas. And, we look forward to serving current and future residents in the manner they deserve for many years to come.”
